milestones.description: Holding has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for WI, going past Faoud Bacchus's 2
Greg Chappell has become the top scorer in ODIs with 867 runs, going past Dennis Amiss's 859
Australia's 8-run win against West Indies is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 31-run win against New Zealand
Ian Chappell has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AUS breaking Greg Chappell's record
